OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1774282275
OL,3,CRobert Mueller, who investigated
OL,4,CRussia-Trump campaign ties, dies aged
OL,5,C81
OL,7,FFormer FBI director Robert Mueller,
OL,8,Fwho later became special counsel in
OL,9,Fcharge of investigating ties between
OL,10,FRussia and Donald Trump's 2016
OL,11,Fpresidential campaign, has died aged
OL,12,F81.
OL,14,F"With deep sadness, we are sharing the
OL,15,Fnews that Bob passed away" on Friday
OL,16,Fnight, his family said in a statement
OL,17,FSaturday.
OL,19,F"His family asks that their privacy be
OL,20,Frespected."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
