PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1774282275
OL,3,CRobert Mueller, who investigated
OL,4,CRussia-Trump campaign ties, dies aged
OL,5,C81
OL,7,FMueller began his 12-year tenure at
OL,8,Fthe FBI just one week before the
OL,9,FSeptember 11 terrorist attacks in 2021.
OL,11,FThe cataclysmic event instantaneously
OL,12,Fswitched the bureau's top priority
OL,13,Ffrom solving domestic crime to
OL,14,Fpreventing terrorism.
OL,16,FHe was nominated by Republican
OL,17,Fpresident George W Bush and went on
OL,18,Fthe serve under Democratic president
OL,19,FBarack Obama, leaving the post in 2013.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1774282275
OL,3,CRobert Mueller, who investigated
OL,4,CRussia-Trump campaign ties, dies aged
OL,5,C81
OL,7,FAfter several years in private
OL,8,Fpractice, Mueller was asked to return
OL,9,Fto public service as special counsel
OL,10,Fin the Justice Department's
OL,11,Finvestigation into whether the Trump
OL,12,Fcampaign illegally coordinated with
OL,13,FRussia to sway the outcome of the 2016
OL,14,Fpresidential race.
OL,16,FHis team spent nearly two years
OL,17,Fquietly conducting one of the most
OL,18,Fconsequential, yet divisive,
OL,19,Finvestigations in Justice Department
OL,20,Fhistory.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1774282275
OL,3,CRobert Mueller, who investigated
OL,4,CRussia-Trump campaign ties, dies aged
OL,5,C81
OL,7,FMueller held no news conferences and
OL,8,Fmade no public appearances during the
OL,9,Finvestigation, remaining quiet despite
OL,10,Fattacks from Trump and his supporters
OL,11,Fand creating an aura of mystery around
OL,12,Fhis work.
OL,14,FAll told, Mueller brought criminal
OL,15,Fcharges against six of the president's
OL,16,Fassociates, including his campaign
OL,17,Fchairman and first national security
OL,18,Fadviser.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1774282275
OL,3,CRobert Mueller, who investigated
OL,4,CRussia-Trump campaign ties, dies aged
OL,5,C81
OL,7,FHis 448-page report, released in April
OL,8,F2019, identified substantial contacts
OL,9,Fbetween the Trump campaign and Russia
OL,10,Fbut did not allege a criminal
OL,11,Fconspiracy.
OL,13,FHe laid out damaging details about
OL,14,FTrump's efforts to seize control of
OL,15,Fthe investigation, and even shut it
OL,16,Fdown, though he declined to decide
OL,17,Fwhether Trump had broken the law, in
OL,18,Fpart because of department policy
OL,19,Fbarring the indictment of a sitting
OL,20,Fpresident.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1774282275
OL,3,CRobert Mueller, who investigated
OL,4,CRussia-Trump campaign ties, dies aged
OL,5,C81
OL,7,FBut, in perhaps the most memorable
OL,8,Flanguage of the report, Mueller
OL,9,Fpointedly noted: "If we had confidence
OL,10,Fafter a thorough investigation of the
OL,11,Ffacts that the president clearly did
OL,12,Fnot commit obstruction of justice, we
OL,13,Fwould so state.
OL,15,F"Based on the facts and the applicable
OL,16,Flegal standards, we are unable to
OL,17,Freach that judgment."
OL,19,FTrump posted on social media about
OL,20,FMueller's death: "Robert Mueller just
OL,21,Fdied. Good, I'm glad he's dead."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1774282275
OL,3,CRobert Mueller, who investigated
OL,4,CRussia-Trump campaign ties, dies aged
OL,5,C81
OL,7,FThe US president added, "He can no
OL,8,Flonger hurt innocent people!"
OL,10,FIn a statement, former Democratic
OL,11,FPresident Barack Obama called Mueller
OL,12,F"one of the finest directors in the
OL,13,Fhistory of the FBI" who saved
OL,14,F"countless lives" after transforming
OL,15,Fthe bureau.
OL,17,F"But it was his relentless commitment
OL,18,Fto the rule of law and his unwavering
OL,19,Fbelief in our bedrock values that made
OL,20,Fhim one of the most respected public
OL,21,Fservants of our time," Obama added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
